Text: As I discovered, there's no US-SI version of Rao's Mechanical Vibrations 4th, only an SI version. The popular solution manual here (uploader abuel-3bbas) is the same SI version as mine (my old early 2010 Demonoid upload actually). With my upload, you get a single clean bookmarked file (10 MB smaller) to which some missing solutions were added and some errors corrected.
